# Guidance on AI Use in Schools
#### Given all of the concerns about AI use in schools - fictions, bias, and data privacy - it’s important for educators to have guidance on the appropriate and responsible use of AI.

#### Check out TeachAI’s <a href="https://www.teachai.org/toolkit-guidance">Guidance on the Use of AI in Our Schools</a>. While you’re reading, think about how the guidance in the toolkit can help mitigate some of the concerns with AI. You'll reflect on this question in the next level.


